  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a68dcd5d31e684d4f8fa33d4ccd3de02, type: 3}
  m_Name: Terzi
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::SoulData
  soulName: Takaba Yuki
  baseSprite: {fileID: 8500104657735791916, guid: da83a39faf0346941814130bfd3013f2, type: 3}
  fullBackstory: "Lakap: Yak\u0131nlardaki En G\xFCvenilir Terzi\n\r\nGe\xE7mi\u015F:
    Bu onun 3. reenkarnesi. Daha \xF6nceki hayatlar\u0131nda da terziydi ve bu durum
    neredeyse hi\xE7 de\u011Fi\u015Fmedi. Her zaman kazand\u0131\u011F\u0131 paralar\u0131n
    fazlas\u0131n\u0131 ihtiya\xE7 sahiplerine ve sokak hayvanlar\u0131na ba\u011F\u0131\u015Flard\u0131,
    ayr\u0131ca dikti\u011Fi k\u0131yafetler insanlar aras\u0131nda \xE7ok ra\u011Fbet
    g\xF6r\xFCrd\xFC.\n\r\n\xD6l\xFCm sebebi: Kanser.\n\r\nSon s\xF6z\xFC: \"Merak
    etme k\u0131z\u0131m, yak\u0131nda iyile\u015Fip seninle bol bol vakit ge\xE7irece\u011Fim.\""
  soulCoins: 8
  dialogueLines:
  - text: Ah... merhaba, ben Yuki.
    emotion: 0
    expression: {fileID: -42354882922023735, guid: 610009c93ffb5ea4a80c5bcde16f04d1, type: 3}
  - text: "\u015Eey, biraz utanmazca olacak ama acaba bir \u015Fekilde k\u0131z\u0131m\u0131n
      yan\u0131nda tekrar reenkarne olma \u015Fans\u0131m var m\u0131?"
    emotion: 4
    expression: {fileID: -42354882922023735, guid: 610009c93ffb5ea4a80c5bcde16f04d1, type: 3}
  - text: "Muhtemelen \u015Fu an d\xFCnyada tek ba\u015F\u0131na kald\u0131, o evlatl\u0131k
      yani benden ba\u015Fka ona bakabilecek kimsesi yok... "
    emotion: 1
    expression: {fileID: -42354882922023735, guid: 610009c93ffb5ea4a80c5bcde16f04d1, type: 3}
  - text: "Ah, can\u0131m k\u0131z\u0131m. Acaba onun yan\u0131na d\xF6nmeme izin
      verir misiniz?"
    emotion: 4
    expression: {fileID: -42354882922023735, guid: 610009c93ffb5ea4a80c5bcde16f04d1, type: 3}
  - text: "Herhangi bir \u015Fekilde ona faydam dokunacaksa her \u015Feye kabul\xFCm..."
    emotion: 1
    expression: {fileID: -42354882922023735, guid: 610009c93ffb5ea4a80c5bcde16f04d1, type: 3}
  optionA:
    lifeLabel: 8
    lifeDescription: "K\u0131z\u0131n\u0131n yan\u0131nda bir k\xF6pek olarak yeniden
      do\u011F"
    coinCost: 8
    bonusSoul: {fileID: 0}
    appearanceDayOffset: 0
  optionB:
    lifeLabel: 3
    lifeDescription: "Japonya'da zengin bir ailede yeniden do\u011F"
    coinCost: 3
    bonusSoul: {fileID: 0}
    appearanceDayOffset: 0
